column5: Hey guy's was thinking about taking a bunch of kids ice fishing for the day, looking for a operator, any suggestions?  Thanks
Terry Goy 905 775 2754.  Gilford ice cabins 705 456 0000  Up the other side of the lake Casey's Port Bolster Inn 705 437 1560. I hope this helps.
On the east side of the lake I recommend Tim Hales or Floyd Hales. I've used Floyd Hales a number of times over the last 20 years but prefer Tims.  Both have their huts in the same general area.
Lucky's Sons near Lefroy.  Still waiting for more ice, but they're posting conditions on the homepage.
J's Fish Huts 705-456-8779  1169 Killarney Beach Road , Lefroy
